The paper proposes a method for modeling real-world multidimensional time series with sporadic observations using a continuous-time version of the Gated Recurrent Unit and a Bayesian update network. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), statistics (cs.ST), control systems (cs.SY), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
